Name: MONTH NAME, ABBREVIATED
Explanation: THE NATO-STANDARD 3-LETTER ABBREVIATED ENGLISH NAME OF A SPECIFIC MONTH, ONE OF THE TWELVE PARTS INTO WHICH A GREGORIAN CALENDAR YEAR IS DIVIDED.

Name: MONTH, NUMERIC
Explanation: A 2-DIGIT NUMERIC REPRESENTATION OF A SPECIFIC MONTH, ONE OF THE TWELVE PARTS INTO WHICH A GREGORIAN CALENDAR YEAR IS DIVIDED.
